4	ASSUMPTIONS
1.	Value date will be defaulted to system date when payment is processed. If required, users can change this date.
2.	Vendor bank details are updated in the Vendor master and no validation will be done in this interface
3.	No inbound files processing is required. Error files will be sent to the business team to take necessary action.
4.	Connectivity between ERP TEST server and NBO TEST server will be available for testing purpose.
5.	Data clean-up, if needed, should be done by business users manually.

